For advice on becoming a teacher, call Get Into Teaching for free on 0800 389 2500 or chat to an adviser online:

https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/contact

For any technical issues using Apply for teacher training, contact us at [becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk](mailto:becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk)

<% else %>

#Are you still interested in teaching?

If now’s the right time for you, you can apply for teacher training again this year.

We’ve saved your last application, so all you have to do is choose a course, review your application and re-submit. You can also take a look at the provider feedback in your account if you want to strengthen your application.

Sign in to review feedback and apply again:
https://www.apply-for-teacher-training.education.gov.uk/candidate/account

# Get help
For advice on becoming a teacher, call Get Into Teaching for free on 0800 389 2500 or chat to an adviser online:
https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/contact

For any technical issues using Apply for teacher training, contact us at [becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk](mailto:becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk)

<% end %>

<% else %>

Dear <%= @application_form.first_name %>,

# <%= 'Application'.pluralize(@declined_course_names.size) %> withdrawn automatically

<% if FeatureFlag.active?('covid_19') %>
We withdrew your application for <%= @declined_course_names.to_sentence %> because you didn’t respond in time.
<% else %>
We withdrew your application for <%= @declined_course_names.to_sentence %> because you didn’t respond to the <%= 'offer'.pluralize(@declined_course_names.size) %> within <%= @declined_courses.first.decline_by_default_days %> working days.
<% end %>

# Give feedback or report a problem

Contact us at [becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk](mailto:becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk)

